snippet.title: Rockman & Forte FC - NCFC 2020 Trailer
snippet.description:
After FC Team's Rockman 7FC and Rockman 8FC, it is time for me to continue the tradition with Rockman & Forte FC, an 8-bit version (and also rebalancing) of Mega Man & Bass!


If you want to know more about it (or want to check out my other fan projects), just join my newly re-worked Unlimited Force Discord server: https://discord.gg/hnyK7JZ


[Trailer was done by j8bit_forager and Duo_GE/M.A.G.E]
